title: LFM Gold + support main.
body:
As title states, looking for a gold + supp to do some ranked 5's today asap.

If youre keen hit me up in game.

Roman numeral 6.

replies.body: Plat 3 support main here, add me if you need a support for 5s.

Gold 3, played alot of SoloQ support, I'm looking for a good ranked 5's team so I can learn to support in 5's.
Sent you a request in game
Hi, I'm Silver 1 Support main, would that suffice?
